PuReMD (Purdue Reactive Molecular Dynamics Program) 
@ref: Aktulga, H. M.; Fogarty, J. C.; Pandit, S. A.; Grama, A. Y. Parallel Computing 2012, 38, 245.
@http: 

We have implemented the Accelerated MD method in PuReMD.


Bond boost method
@ ref: J. Chem. Phys. 119. 6210 (2003)

keywords in control

bboost           1 ! 0: no bond boost; 1: bond boost simulation
bboost_Vmax      200.0 ! bond boost maximium boost potential
bboost_P1        0.95 ! bond boost adjust parameter
bboost_q         0.3  ! bond boost switch



